text: László Nyers (14 April 1934 - 22 January 2013) was a Hungarian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle +97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Hungary Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Somogy County
